741
00:58:54,347 --> 00:58:58,545
...was at home that Saturday afternoon
and evening, then?

742
00:59:00,153 --> 00:59:01,484
Yes.

743
00:59:01,854 --> 00:59:06,518
I will remind the witness
that she is under oath...

744
00:59:06,693 --> 00:59:08,024
...and ask her again.

745
00:59:08,194 --> 00:59:13,689
Edna Hooper, will you swear that during
the hours when this indictment...

746
00:59:13,866 --> 00:59:16,926
