and I shall order the courtroom cleared.

843
01:05:13,426 --> 01:05:15,257
- Proceed.
- May it please the court.

844
01:05:16,596 --> 01:05:18,393
The state's own witnesses...

845
01:05:18,564 --> 01:05:22,125
...have not been able to identify
these defendants...

846
01:05:22,301 --> 01:05:25,168
...as having even been
at the scene of the crime...

